{
  "stem": "1736.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 232.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was a different understanding in orthodoxy in-- in Germany in those days to what it is today.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a practicing Jew, though.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a practicing Jew, that's right, keeping Shabbat and all that, but not going with the whole Polish traditions of-- of ear locks and beard, and-- you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess, in our religion, everybody has our own ways of saying, this is how much I keep, and this one I don't keep, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was coming back to this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very friendly with the boys in the street, and we used to go here and there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that went on fine until I was to go into this higher school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by then, of course, things have got worse, in 1937.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this is what I'm coming to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's when things started to become obvious to me, things like [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] teachers singling me out, saying, you didn't do this right, you didn't do that right, and all this sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Other things--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the one that really-- besides little things-- that really sticks in my mind was that-- and I mentioned that before, that Aken is on the Elbe, which is a very long, big river.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a swimming pool there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as part of the schooling, seven children our age were meant to be taught swimming.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not like it is today, that every second house has a swimming pool.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the only facility there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember going there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm talking about '37.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born '26, if my arithmetic is right.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
